{"tid":2486602,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[新聞] 自稱是哈利波特 美國「石內卜」撞死紐約知名法官","createTime":"2021-04-13T04:02:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-13T11:31:44.000Z","uid":66351,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ed5ed5fa27947fe2d394a0cbd1599428ef3840ee","tid":2486602,"uid":66351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T04:02:06.000Z","msg":"美國女駕駛石內卜（Nastasia Snape），在佛州開車撞死75歲聯邦法官費爾斯坦（Sandra Feuerstein），<span class=\"red\">她在肇事後自稱是「哈利波特」</span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmdb52gn7PjWscJ5ceB1AbRuFq5pzVk9RkXJGvX88Jg4LP?filename=yjhy27d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyjhy27d.jpg&h=fced637a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據《ABC》報導，費爾斯坦當時正在佛州度假，9日上午10時許她在人行道上散步，這時由23歲女嫌石內卜（Nastasia Snape）駕駛的紅色雙門轎車竟一路橫衝直撞開了上來，撞飛費爾斯坦。<br />\n<br />\n嫌犯肇事後還一路開了8公里左右，直到撞車後才停住。警方透露，石內卜當時在車內似乎昏迷不醒，但執勤人員走近轎車時，石內卜又恢復意識從車上下來，身體出現了類似癲癇的抽搐動作。<br />\n<br />\n現場警察曾嘗試與石內卜交談，不過她拒絕回答問題，只是兩眼無神地一直放空，當救護人員準備將其送醫時，<span class=\"red\">石內卜突然情緒激動地大吼大叫，自稱是「哈利波特」並和醫療人員扭打在一起，最終動用了麻醉劑才制伏住石內卜</span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n在這起事故中不幸身亡的費爾斯坦，歷來擔任拿索郡、紐約地方法官與紐約最高法院法官，2003年被時任總統的小布希任命為聯邦法官。"},{"pid":"ec8e6bdb660bf5968e914887e67a09efac3f6e6b","tid":2486602,"uid":199893,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T04:08:50.000Z","msg":"石內卜唔想做配角<br />\n想做主角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cbec9c4c5155177dfa0e399e424aa1b41c4b2db","tid":2486602,"uid":82879,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T04:10:57.000Z","msg":"入嚟先睇得明標題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dd74aa3391dc56f6e156e3b65f81f9ce0c699c3","tid":2486602,"uid":110832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T04:11:50.000Z","msg":"黑命貴"},{"pid":"f29d0521700f7be2bc8dc2c3214ad8b689616494","tid":2486602,"uid":309553,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T04:13:28.000Z","msg":"黑魔法師"},{"pid":"8f5dab02dc28ab16e15ef1d055cc2d0bf44d77f1","tid":2486602,"uid":76657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T04:17:21.000Z","msg":"第一段睇錯美女駕駛"},{"pid":"66b712c6c7a354f17e43a7cc8de7b41c65308abd","tid":2486602,"uid":116143,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T04:18:50.000Z","msg":"又係下三白<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2568bc3dac4145fe035b336c484dec56121de29","tid":2486602,"uid":25559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T04:55:06.000Z","msg":"blm"},{"pid":"07f62292aec843b45653ae5f5ba17b6112e538f9","tid":2486602,"uid":375787,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T11:19:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media1.tenor.com/images/8f7a28e62f8242b264c8a39ba8bea261/tenor.gif?itemid=15922897\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia1.tenor.com%2Fimages%2F8f7a28e62f8242b264c8a39ba8bea261%2Ftenor.gif%3Fitemid%3D15922897&h=8c80ac42&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"438201cfbea0d509043a164d9742aec10d69f102","tid":2486602,"uid":185651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66b712c6c7a354f17e43a7cc8de7b41c65308abd","tid":2486602,"uid":116143,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T04:18:50.000Z","msg":"又係下三白<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T11:31:44.000Z","msg":"雙目無神 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}